posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!!!', 'Ask for ID# 4903A', 'Welcome home.', 'Our 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments for rent put you right at the heart of this up-and-coming neighborhood, with close proximity to retail, entertainment, and dining at The Woodlands, as well as just a short drive to the vibrant culture of downtown Houston.', 'Our pet-friendly community features a resort-style pool with private cabanas and a brand-new fitness studio complete with cardio, Pilates, and circuit training equipment.', 'Our on-site water park and resident club lounge mean you won’t even have to leave home to have a thrilling weekend.', 'Stainless-Steel Energy-Efficient Appliances', 'Granite Counters', 'Air Conditioning', 'Upgraded Light Fixtures and Ceiling Fans', 'Custom Cabinetry', 'Luxury Bathrooms with Granite Countertops and Tile Floors', 'Garden-Sized Soaking Tub and Glass Shower', 'Fully Equipped Kitchen', 'Dishwasher', 'Open Floor Plans with Expansive Windows', 'Fireplace', 'Private Balcony/Patio', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Washer & Dryer', 'Hardwood Flooring', 'Nine-Foot Ceilings', 'Under-Counter Lighting', 'Tile Backsplash in Kitchen', 'Oversized Doors']
